replies.body:
Ahem. I'm speaking of those that joined the game recently. They aren't given a chance to get limited items that were available before they joined. Or they couldn't achieve Gold rank.

 Riot- "Oh, you came in after that skin was available? Nope! Sorry, you can't have it, you have to wait for the next one to come, or if you want a Victorious skin, good luck getting to Gold because we let ragers, AFKers, and others like them screw you out of any chance getting there. We also don't punish them or balance the game effectively. Welcome to League of Legends, where you will get addicted, spend hundreds of dollars that fuel our non existent care for you as we sit back and laugh while you rage! Have a fun time!" {{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}} 


Sarcasm aside, it's bullshit how Riot does things.
